    "scrollHeight": 115,
    "scrollWidth": 614,
    "top": 2969.453125,
    "width": 614,
    "x": 422,
    "y": 2969.453125,
    "text": "When asked for comment, Meta referred Business Insider to comments earlier this year from Zuckerberg that 2026 is the year AI will begin to \"dramatically change the way we work,\" with projects that once required large teams potentially handled by one, \"very talented\" person."
  },
  {
